  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the morbidity and mortality of patients who have undergone percutaneous
      tracheostomy due to respiratory failure in the critical care unit and after intensive care in
      the internal medicine department, including follow-up of quality of life of these patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
